data.description: ?? Welcome to Your Dream Home in Summerfield Place! ??  Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this move-in-ready gem located at 222 Denning Drive, Houma, LA, in the sought-after Summerfield Place Subdivision.  Property Features: - 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms - 1801 sqft of Living Space - Inviting Inground Pool - Cozy Fireplace - Elegant Granite Countertops  Prime Location: Situated in a family-friendly neighborhood, enjoy the convenience of stores, schools, and parks within walking distance.  Move-In Ready: This home is ready for you to make memories! The master bathroom has been recently renovated, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.  Exceptional Living Spaces: The large living area provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The eat-in kitchen, complete with granite countertops, is a culinary haven for family meals and gatherings.  Outdoor Oasis: Step outside to your private inground pool, offering the perfect escape for sunny Louisiana days.  New List Price: Priced at $255,000, this home is a fantastic investment for those seeking both comfort and value.  Contact Information: ?? Call or text Mercy Davis at (985) 860-5061   ?? Email: mercy.davis@exprealty.com  Don't miss the opportunity to call 222 Denning Drive your home. Schedule your showing today and experience the charm of Summerfield Place living! ???? #HoumaLiving #DreamHome #SummerfieldPlace
